        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer36216540" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3436542891362209016">A compelling history of the impact of the West on the Congo</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

