    <a title="Lee Prescott" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/125242563-lee-prescott"><img alt="Lee Prescott" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1608814536p2/125242563.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
