<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/185540.The_Fate_of_Africa"><img alt="The Fate of Africa: A History of Fifty Years of Independence" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1442953695l/185540._SX98_.jpg" />
